#

Pasta Carbonara

25 min
$8.5
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

GlutenDairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

QuickComfort Food

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main

Tags:

ItalianPastaEasy

Description

A creamy, savory pasta dish made with eggs, cheese, pancetta, and pepper, perfect for a quick indulgent meal.

Ingredients

  • spaghetti: 200g
  • pancetta or bacon: 100g
  • eggs: 2 large
  • parmesan cheese: 50g, grated
  • black pepper: to taste
  • salt: to taste
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
